# Code owners for Terraform Healer
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global owners - will be requested for review on all PRs
* @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Core source code
/src/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Kubernetes manifests
/k8s/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# CI/CD workflows
/.github/workflows/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Documentation - can have different reviewers
/docs/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Security sensitive files
/SECURITY.md @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
/Dockerfile @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
